text: Carlos Ramón Aranguiz Zúñiga (18 September 1953 - 3 January 2021) was a Chilean politician and lawyer. He was born in Antofagasta, Chile. He was a member of the Supreme Court of Chile from 2014 until his death. Aránguiz died on 3 January 2021 in Antofagasta from pulmonary fibrosis, aged 67.Tras una larga enfermedad fallece el supremo Carlos Aránguiz, el exministro en visita del polémico Caso Coimas ==References== Category:1953 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Deaths from pulmonary fibrosis Category:Chilean politicians Category:Chilean lawyers
